      "content": "oh okay thanks. so just as a heads up, if i do accidentally take them together and i start feeling some mild achiness in my legs or a bit of fatigue, is that just normal side effects or should i be worried? can i just take some ibuprofen and ride it out until the antibiotics are done?",
